        <problem_statement>When communities face challenges—such as waste accumulation, seasonal disease outbreaks, or natural disasters—citizens are often willing to help but lack a centralized way to coordinate efforts effectively.&#13;
Existing social media platforms are good for awareness, but they lack structured task management, volunteer tracking, and impact measurement capabilities.&#13;
There’s a need for a digital platform that can connect volunteers, NGOs, and local authorities, enabling organized and timely community action.</problem_statement>
